HEADWORD: Endenizen
<hw>En*den"i*zen</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>en-</ets> + <ets>denizen</ets>. Cf. <er>Indenizen</er>.]</ety>
<def>To admit to the privileges of a denizen; to naturalize.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>B. Jonson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

